1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
各位大英姐妹早晨

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Good morning brothers and sisters

3
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,000
我們在港澳之先再一次同心低頭祈禱

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Let's pray

5
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:10,000
蔡恩主我們感謝你

6
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Father God thank you so much

7
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:15,000
因為你是我們唯一食不敬拜的真神

8
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Because you are the one true God that we worship

9
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,000
你吩咐我們

10
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,000
You have commanded us

11
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,000
你都告訴我們有異象問就滅亡

12
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
You've told us that without vision that we will perish

13
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,000
求天賦你的靈

14
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
現在在我們的心靈裏面

15
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,000
開啟我們的心靈

16
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:37,000
May the spirit of you, the Father, open the spirit in us

17
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:39,000
主啊求你的靈向向我們說話

18
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,000
May your spirit speak to us

19
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,000
祈禱奉教主耶穌基督的名靠

20
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,000
In Jesus' name we pray

21
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Amen

22
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:51,000
我想有一段經文大家很熟悉的

23
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
I think there is a verse that is very familiar to all of us

24
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,000
就說按著命定人人都有一死

25
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,000
死後且有審判

26
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,000
It says and just as it is appointed for man to die once

27
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,000
and after that comes judgment

28
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:11,000
所以我們每一個人都會有一天要交帳的

29
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:13,000
So one day we are accountable to God

30
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,000
and we have to look at the past

31
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:19,000
而我們每一個人都要明白就是

32
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,000
我們在世界上所做的事

33
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,000
和所作的決定

34
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:27,000
無論是善惡都會被神去檢視

35
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,000
So one day there will be judgment

36
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,000
God will judge all that we do

37
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:34,000
whether it is good or it is evil

38
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,000
所以死後且有審判

39
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,000
意思就是說我們會有後果的

40
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:41,000
When there comes judgment after death

41
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,000
it means that there are consequences

42
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,000
所以對我們每個記憶圖來說

43
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,000
我們知道這個福音的必需性

44
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,000
So to us Christians

45
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:53,000
we have to know the necessity of the gospel

46
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,000
因為唯有我們得著基督

47
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,000
在受審判的時候

48
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,000
我們才可以無罪釋放

49
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,000
Because as we know

50
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,000
only when we know Christ as our Lord

51
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:06,000
that when we get judged that will be saved

52
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,000
另外一段經文大家很熟悉的就是說

53
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,000
趁著白日

54
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:12,000
我們必須做猜我來的那位的工

55
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,000
黑夜來到就沒有人能做工了

56
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Another familiar verse says we must work

57
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
the works of Him who sent me while it is day

58
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:25,000
night is coming when no one can work

59
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
白日

60
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
daylight

61
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:31,000
可能是說我們還有在世在生的日子

62
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:34,000
Maybe it means that we are still living on earth

63
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:37,000
也代表著神的恩典還存在

64
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,000
讓我們可以去回應祂

65
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,000
Maybe it means that God's grace is still here

66
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,000
that we can respond to Him

67
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,000
當黑夜來到

68
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,000
But when night comes

69
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,000
我們的生命沒有了

70
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,000
When we die

71
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,000
完結了

72
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,000
When we end

73
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:54,000
我們神的恩典

74
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:58,000
我們不在神的恩典的時代裡面的時候

75
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:01,000
Maybe we are not in the era of God's grace

76
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,000
黑夜來到沒有人能做工了

77
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,000
The night is here and no one can work

78
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,000
所以有一個時效性的

79
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,000
So there is a limit of time

80
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:13,000
所以這段經文也提醒我和你把握時機

81
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:16,000
就因為福音是有一個迫切性的

82
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,000
This verse also tells us that we have to seize the divine moment

83
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:22,000
because there is an urgency of the gospel

84
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,000
但我和你相信了一段時間的話

85
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:28,000
So you and I have become Christians for some time

86
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:31,000
有時候我們日復一日這樣生活

87
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Maybe day after day we live just as usual

88
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,000
我們會看到有機會來

89
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,000
有機會過去

90
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:40,000
We see opportunities come and opportunities go

91
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:43,000
我們錯過這次的機會

92
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,000
我們下次再等下下次機會

93
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,000
Maybe we miss this opportunity

94
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,000
