95
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,000
但是聖經告訴我們那個迫切性

96
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,000
But the Bible tells us there is an urgency

97
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,000
是一個神聖的時刻

98
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,000
And it is a divine moment

99
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:00,000
是有一個機會這段時間裡面你需要去做的

100
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,000
And there is an opportunity that we have to seize

101
